#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:2 ../components/nitrophone/index.rst:19
msgid "Apps"
msgstr "Apps"

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:5
msgid "App Store"
msgstr "App Store"

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:7
msgid ""
"For very high security requirements, you should use as few apps as "
"possible to provide a small attack surface. If instead you want to use "
"the NitroPhone as an everyday smartphone with more apps we recommend:"
msgstr ""
"Bei sehr hohen Sicherheitsanforderungen solltest du so wenige Apps wie "
"möglich verwenden, um eine kleine Angriffsfläche zu bieten. Wenn du das "
"NitroPhone stattdessen als Alltags-Smartphone mit mehr Apps nutzen willst, "
"empfehlen wir:"

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:11
msgid ""
"Install the `F-Droid <https://f-droid.org/F-Droid.apk>`__ App Store. This"
" has exclusively open source apps that do without drastic tracking and "
"without advertising. Here you will find thousands of apps from a wide "
"variety of fields. If you are looking for an app, check F-Droid first."
msgstr ""
"Installiere den `F-Droid <https://f-droid.org/F-Droid.apk>`__ App Store. "
"Dieser hat ausschließlich Open-Source-Apps, die ohne drastisches Tracking "
"und ohne Werbung auskommen. Hier findest du Tausende von Apps aus den "
"verschiedensten Bereichen. Wenn du auf der Suche nach einer App bist, schau "
"zuerst bei F-Droid nach."

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:16
msgid ""
"If the apps in F-Droid are not enough for you, open F-Droid and install "
"Aurora Store. In Aurora Store, you can install all apps from Google Play "
"Store."
msgstr ""
"Wenn dir die Apps in F-Droid nicht ausreichen, öffne F-Droid und installiere "
"den Aurora Store. Im Aurora Store kannst du alle Apps aus dem Google Play "
"Store installieren."

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:19
msgid ""
"Many apps work without Google Play Services. However, if you want to use "
"apps that require Google Play Services, you can install `Google Play "
"Services in a sandbox <https://grapheneos.org/usage#sandboxed-google-"
"play>`__ as follows."
msgstr ""
"Viele Apps funktionieren auch ohne Google Play Services. Wenn du jedoch Apps "
"verwenden möchtest, die Google Play Services benötigen, kannst du die Google "
"Play Services in einer Sandbox <https://grapheneos.org/usage#sandboxed-"
"google-play>`__ wie folgt installieren."

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:22
msgid "Open Graphenes app repository client: *Home screen -> Apps*"
msgstr "Öffne den Graphenes App Repository Client: *Startbildschirm -> Apps*"

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:23
msgid ""
"Install the 3 core Google Play Apps (\"Google Play store\", \"Google Play"
" Services\", \"Google Services Framework\")."
msgstr ""
"Installiere die 3 wichtigsten Google Play Apps (\"Google Play Store\", "
"\"Google Play Services\", \"Google Services Framework\")."

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:24
msgid ""
"Disable batterie optimization for Google Play Services (for Push to work "
"properly). From the home screen, select: *Settings -> Apps -> Google Play"
" services > Battery > Unrestricted*"
msgstr ""
"Deaktiviere die Batterieoptimierung für Google Play Services (damit Push "
"richtig funktioniert). Wähle auf dem Startbildschirm: *Einstellungen -> Apps "
"-> Google Play-Dienste > Akku > Uneingeschränkt*"

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:25
msgid ""
"Open the Google Play Store once and press \"Sign in\" to start the "
"initialization. You don't have to finish the sign in and a real login is "
"not necessary. This is solely to initialize the software."
msgstr ""
"Öffne einmal den Google Play Store und klicke auf \"Anmelden\", um die "
"Initialisierung zu starten. Du musst die Anmeldung nicht abschließen und "
"eine echte Anmeldung ist nicht notwendig. Dies dient nur der Initialisierung "
"der Software."

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:30
msgid ""
"To prevent some apps from accessing Google Play Services, install Google "
"Play Services in a separate profile. To do this, create a new dedicated "
"user profile and install the Google Play Services there. Using a work "
"profile together with *Shelter* is also possible, but without as much "
"isolation."
msgstr ""
"Um zu verhindern, dass einige Apps auf die Google Play Services zugreifen, "
"installiere die Google Play Services in einem separaten Profil. Dazu "
"erstellst du ein neues, eigenes Nutzerprofil und installierst die Google "
"Play Services dort. Die Verwendung eines Arbeitsprofils zusammen mit "
"*Shelter* ist auch möglich, allerdings ohne so viel Isolierung."

#: ../components/nitrophone/apps.rst:38
msgid ""
"The Google Play Store cannot install and update apps due to the sandbox. "
"Instead, always use F-Droid (for open source apps) or Aurora Store (for "
"apps from Google Play Store) to install apps."
msgstr ""
"Der Google Play Store kann aufgrund der Sandbox keine Apps installieren und "
"aktualisieren. Verwende stattdessen immer F-Droid (für Open Source Apps) "
"oder Aurora Store (für Apps aus dem Google Play Store), um Apps zu "
"installieren."

